   MOVIE-REVIEWS-DAYTON
</P>
<P>
   ANTZ-DDN _ The ants come marching two-by-two, preparing to do
battle in the nation's theaters. DreamWorks' Antz , a
computer-animated insect adventure featuring the voices of Woody
Allen, Sylvester Stallone and Sharon Stone, tromps into theaters
today. Disney's A Bug's Life , a similarly styled film from the
creators of Toy Story , follows on its six heels on Nov. 25.
(Larsen, Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
