friendly PAX TV's show ``It's a Miracle,'' Paxson Communications
Chairman Lowell ``Bud'' Paxson said recently. Thomas joins actress
Nia Peeples as co-host of the show, replacing country singer Billy
Dean. The change is set for this Sunday Oct. 4. (Plunkett, Palm
Beach Post) MOVED.
