 ART ADV.: Photos with EXPLOSIVE-CHILD, ALASKA-HIGHWAY and
HOME-CHENILLE are being transmitted to NYT Photo Service
subscribers.  
 For Immediate Release  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Boston Globe plans to move the following FEATURE stories for
use by NYTimes News Service clients.
</P>
<P>
