   &UR; Other international &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL-CHEMWAR (Jerusalem) _ The Israeli airline, El Al, admits
that the cargo plane that crashed near Amsterdam in 1992 was
carrying chemicals used for chemcial weapons. By Joel Greenberg.
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-ECON (Moscow) _ The new Russian Cabinet discusses a
statist economic plan. By Michael R. Gordon.
</P>
<P>
   BRAZIL-ELECT (Rio de Janeiro) _ With a presidential election on
Sunday, Brazilians who were feeling flush after the taming of
hyperinflation now feel they've tumbled down the economic ladder.
By Diana Jean Schemo.
</P>
