<SLUG> BC-BAND-BREAKUP-ART-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IT'S ALL OVER FOR THE REFRESHMENTS  
 (ART ADV: PHOTO HAS BEEN SENT TO NYTNS CLIENTS) 
