<P>
   TRAVEL-BRIEFS-NYT (Undated) _ Warnings to passengers after
Bahamas murders; Names of next of kin requested for flights; Autumn
leaves, seen from a train; Frequent-flier miles; ceramics from the
Marina Picasso collection.
</P>
