dumpster. ``I just love doing this,'' she said. The object of
Rose's affection is her new home-style paper shredder, a
convenience that's fast becoming more common in Arizona households
than bread machines and expresso makers. With PHOTO. By LINDA
HELSER. Story moved in the ``L'' category. &QL; 
